                <text>Analysts noted yesterday that Cray Research-1's decision *trace*-1 to
                    link its $98.3 million promissory note to Mr. Cray's presence will
                    complicate a valuation of the new company.
                </text>
                <arg f="" n="0">*trace*</arg>
                <rel f="">link</rel>
                <arg f="" n="1">its $98.3 million promissory note</arg>
